OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779894668
OL,3,CDonaldson arrives at court ahead of
OL,4,Cprosecution opening in sexual offences
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FFormer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson has arrived at court in
OL,9,FNewry ahead of the prosecution opening
OL,10,Fits case in his trial over alleged
OL,11,Fhistorical sexual offences.
OL,13,FThe start of the case on Wednesday was
OL,14,Fdelayed until after lunch amid legal
OL,15,Fdiscussions.
OL,17,FDonaldson, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,18,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
