FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779894668
OL,3,CDonaldson arrives at court ahead of
OL,4,Cprosecution opening in sexual offences
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,8,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,9,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,10,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008 involving
OL,11,Ftwo alleged victims.
OL,13,FDonaldson's wife Lady Eleanor
OL,14,FDonaldson denies several charges of
OL,15,Faiding and abetting her husband's
OL,16,Falleged offending.
OL,18,FThe 60-year-old is facing a trial of
OL,19,Fthe facts, not a criminal trial, after
OL,20,Fjudge Ramsey ruled her unfit to stand
OL,21,Ftrial on mental health grounds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779894668
OL,3,CDonaldson arrives at court ahead of
OL,4,Cprosecution opening in sexual offences
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe trial of the facts will test the
OL,8,Fevidence in the case but cannot result
OL,9,Fin a criminal conviction.
OL,11,FIt is being heard by the same jury,
OL,12,Fwith proceedings against both
OL,13,FDonaldsons running simultaneously as
OL,14,Fpart of one overall trial process
OL,15,Fpresided over by judge Ramsey.
OL,17,FThe trial is expected to last between
OL,18,Fthree and four weeks.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
