PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779894668
OL,3,CDonaldson arrives at court ahead of
OL,4,Cprosecution opening in sexual offences
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,8,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,9,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,10,FMarch 2024.
OL,12,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,13,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,14,Fallegations emerged.
OL,16,FWeeks before his arrest, he had led
OL,17,Fthe DUP back into devolved government
OL,18,Fat Stormont after a two-year boycott
OL,19,Fof the powersharing institutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
